longName: Holistic Asset Finance Group Co., Ltd.
longBusinessSummary: Holistic Asset Finance Group Co., Ltd. sells radio and airline magazine advertising. It has rights to manage and sell 80 pages per month of advertising for Hainan Airline Group's back of seat magazine; and 108 minutes of advertising per day or 39,420 minutes per year on Tianjin based channel, FM 92.5, and Xi'an based channel, FM 95.5. The company was formerly known as Legend Media, Inc. and changed its name to Holistic Asset Finance Group Co., Ltd. in December 2019. Holistic Asset Finance Group Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 2005 and is based in New York, New York.
